{"tid":484570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"２０１０　動畫版＿高登的街角","createTime":"2017-11-30T08:03:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-30T08:19:06.000Z","uid":141461,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f0c5a65f5761b1064b804183b867f0cd0ee2178f","tid":484570,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T08:03:50.000Z","msg":"２０１０<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Hct6msDWKhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHct6msDWKhk&d=pN576KrB24uCbIBGki5f2wCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=c1fd4a94\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Hct6msDWKhk</a><br />\n<br />\n２０１１<br />\n<br />\n[高登音樂台] 明將戰友<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mKuquiAdKWo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmKuquiAdKWo&d=pN576KrB24uCbIBGki5f2wCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=fd69fcd9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mKuquiAdKWo</a><br />\n<br />\n２０１２<br />\n蝗蟲天下<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ueNr7mfFZu8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DueNr7mfFZu8&d=pN576KrB24uCbIBGki5f2wCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=268926c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ueNr7mfFZu8</a><br />\n<br />\n２０１２<br />\n高登人集體登報反雙非孕婦事件源自網民在2012年1月末於高登討論區及facebook發起的登報行動，內容為反對雙非孕婦來香港產子，以及要求政府修改《基本法》，堵塞「雙非人」子女獲居港權的漏洞。此次登報的導火線為高登大戰香港生兒育女社區的延伸事件。<br />\n<br />\n登報活動發起人林早逝二世（高登會員編號：297595），除了透過高登帖子集資登報，亦在Facebook開設相關活動。[2]他表示登報行動發起僅五天，即籌得十萬元，足夠在報章刊登聲明，涉及 800多名捐款者。[3]<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/s4007E0be9e00b60ee63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fs4007E0be9e00b60ee63.jpg&h=013c415d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[高登音樂台] [情人節年度特別企劃] 毒男宅女10分鐘大合唱 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aFd8jIuCtbo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DaFd8jIuCtbo&d=pN576KrB24uCbIBGki5f2wCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=b22cce64\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aFd8jIuCtbo</a><br />\n<br />\n進擊的蝗蟲<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l6yAD59_Lu8&amp;t=1s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dl6yAD59_Lu8%26t%3D1s&d=pN576KrB24uCbIBGki5f2wCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=b330bcf7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l6yAD59_Lu8&amp;t=1s</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n亳無置疑<br />\n２０１０&mdash;２０１２　<br />\n高登高質到痴撚線<br />\n<br />\n２０１３年開始走下坡"},{"pid":"b040cf571fe6b5e8a5207d66d2194dd5ce8c42ed","tid":484570,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T08:06:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3_yCKsqAhZg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3_yCKsqAhZg&d=pN576KrB24uCbIBGki5f2wCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=6cae7689\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3_yCKsqAhZg</a>"},{"pid":"2da2f3e831c61bd3f09b9c39df3347ccc01248e2","tid":484570,"uid":141461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T08:07:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/3_yCKsqAhZg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3_yCKsqAhZg&d=pN576KrB24uCbIBGki5f2wCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=6cae7689\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3_yCKsqAhZg</a></blockquote><br />\n垃圾到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbb8f0dd832f5102ae5d8e5810d9257b1faa7d11","tid":484570,"uid":41375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T08:08:07.000Z","msg":"香港電影收皮<br />\n音樂收皮<br />\n電視劇收皮<br />\n動畫漫畫收皮<br />\n傳統文化收皮<br />\n依家連網絡文化都收皮<br />\n<br />\n香港文化已死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a841266a87a3c0f17b10b92b7d021bc6787ee88b","tid":484570,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T08:08:33.000Z"